Hello! I&rsquo;m looking to form a group of mature players that would want to practice in a premade 5s environment and potentially, after working out kinks, make a 5s Team. As the title indicated &ndash; this is really for those that get shut out, but still want to improve! I&rsquo;ll add everyone if there is interest in this and ask them the times and days that work for them, but I&rsquo;d hope to aim for 3 nights a week for 3 hours each with breaks in between games. Also - manners are important. Playful jokes are fine, but full rage is no good! ADD in game IF u got Q&#039;s Write below

Post filling out the following if you seem it is worth your time~

In Game Name &ndash;
Age &ndash;
Willing to use Skype/curse/discord voice chat (y/n) &ndash;
Role Preferences (Order Them) &ndash;
Willing to swap between playing your top 2-3 roles (y/n) &ndash;

Favorite Champions Per Role &ndash;
[Mid]
[Top]
[Jungle]
[ADC]
[Support]
Anything you&rsquo;d like to add~~?

&bull;It is important for us to have good team comps, but no one should be forced into a champion that they hate. We&rsquo;d just rotate roles based on what we need if people were willing and had the champions for it.

